												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Trying to stay her usual self, but her mask is cracking a tiny bit here. Privately, Aylin is dealing with a great deal of anger toward her mother, the goddess Selune, But she's not yet willing to face it. How could her powerful mother let all this happen to her?"
